tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE time_series_data (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    value FLOAT,
    PRIMARY KEY (timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE TimeSeriesData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE ForecastingData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    forecast_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE PredictiveAnalytics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    prediction VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE Metadata (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    description VARCHAR
)
